{"tid":2498543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拗柴睇鐵打","createTime":"2021-04-21T08:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T09:47:22.000Z","uid":370141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9bccbcc05245fcfa805e07eb09e69933d38d8002","tid":2498543,"uid":370141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"入到去聽啲人講嘢 <br />\n鐵打師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 病人a<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n病人a：我前日跌親，膝頭哥腫曬行路好痛<br />\n<br />\n鐵打師傅：哦～啲瘀血好腫，去照咗x光未啊？<br />\n<br />\n病人a：吓！？！？睇鐵打都要照x光，咁點解我唔睇物理治療或者西醫？？？<br />\n<br />\n鐵打師傅：咁有x光先知你出現咩問題㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n我：咁以前睇鐵打點算？<br />\n<br />\n鐵打師傅：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞到我最後諗咗好耐幾時應該睇鐵打幾時應該去醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671f3a217a68ccdcd7696517fc711d9bd4c5d619","tid":2498543,"uid":264121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"其實正路係睇左西醫照下先再睇鐵打"},{"pid":"0c91e3536a1c572a6a2c2dcf5a60038a4e6801e4","tid":2498543,"uid":370141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"671f3a217a68ccdcd7696517fc711d9bd4c5d619","tid":2498543,"uid":264121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"其實正路係睇左西醫照下先再睇鐵打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"咁以前未有x光年代點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5b5b144260d9dd45d1b5a09626830a3aa165e0","tid":2498543,"uid":264121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c91e3536a1c572a6a2c2dcf5a60038a4e6801e4","tid":2498543,"uid":370141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"671f3a217a68ccdcd7696517fc711d9bd4c5d619","tid":2498543,"uid":264